@host = http://localhost:8080

### View cart (Thymeleaf)
GET {{host}}/cart
Accept: text/html

### Add product to cart (Referer 없으면 redirect:null 될 수 있음 → 헤더 넣어두는게 안전)
POST {{host}}/cart/add/1?quantity=2
Referer: {{host}}/products/1

### Edit quantity
POST {{host}}/cart/edit/1?quantity=3

### Select / Unselect (boolean param)
POST {{host}}/cart/select/1?checked=true

### Delete cart item
POST {{host}}/cart/delete/1
